Name: Dark Parables: Curse of Briar Rose Collector's Edition
About the game: 1000 years ago, Sleeping Beauty was kissed by a prince, which removed a terrible curse from the kingdom. The rampant briars were held at bay, but the poor princess was left in her slumber. Follow a modern day detective as he travels to Edinburgh, Scotland, and attempts to end the curse once and for all in Dark Parables: Curse of Briar Rose. Dive into this eerie Hidden Object Adventure game and save Sleeping Beauty today! Experience all the exclusive Collector’s Edition extras! The Collector’s Edition includes: Exclusive advanced levels for extra gameplay Interactive Strategy Guide Animated screensaver and wallpapers 3 Briar Rose Novels
